  "description": "An externally attractive, roomy and easy-to-use two-chamber refrigerator with separate cooling circuits for the working chambers. The model was introduced to the market by the popular South Korean brand Samsung in 2024 and is positioned by the manufacturer in the upper price range. The refrigeration system operates on a Digital Inverter compressor, the compressor noise does not exceed 35 dB. The rear part of the case is insulated with a special pad, making it possible to place the device close to walls and furniture. The two-chamber refrigerator Samsung Grand + RB38C602EB1 is equipped with an intelligent energy saving program Tryb AI. The average annual energy consumption is at the level of 211 kW * h. The total useful capacity of the compartments reaches 390 liters, of which 114 liters fall on the freezer located below. Integrated hidden handles are provided for the door leaves. The doors can open in any direction, depending on the side of the hinge installation. The cooling system is based on All Around Cooling technology - a cold flow is supplied to the products from all sides, which allows for quick and efficient cooling of the entire space.",
